---
title: Pork and Apple Meatloaf with Creamy Mashed Potatoes and Green Salad
description: Nothing screams fall more than apples, and nothing pairs better with apples than pork. For this recipe, our chefs chose the Granny Smith variety for its hard, crisp, and slightly tart flesh. When it’s shredded and mixed with pork, the result is a deliciously juicy meatloaf your kids will love.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-meatloaf-with-apples-family-0e275555.jpg
